<plot>Julià, a dynamic, naughty and very vital boy, is diagnosed as having AIDS. His parents do all they can to go ahead with their life, but the rejection they find in their little community, of which they had felt a part of until then, will lead them to a crisis. Finally, the attitude of children of the town, with Cosme - Julià's friend - as their leader, will be a lesson for the whole town.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?019045</url></doc>
